data.description: Fantastic Floor Plan, Huge Bedrooms. Master Bedroom is supersize with a factory built fireplace, 2 closets both walkins and a huge sitting area to completely relax. Upstairs features 3 additional bedrooms that accomdates kingsize bedroom suites. The laundry room is upstairs with an additional full size bath and linen closets. Downstairs features a bedroom and full bath, living room and dining seperate. The kitchen loaded with cabinets, an island, gas stove/oven combo, microwave. Eat in kitchen. One step into the huge family room for big family gathering. The back yard is enclosed with a privacy fence and concrete patio which is the length of the house. The Property is price to sell, As Is. You can make this your own
